headline: Suzano & Kimberly-Clark to Form Global Tissue Joint Venture
summary: SUZ teams up with Kimberly-Clark to form a $3.4B global tissue JV spanning more than 70 countries and 22 facilities.

headline: Kimberly-Clark, Suzano form $3.4B tissue joint venture
summary: The combined company will help alleviate volatile input costs sparked by recent tariffs, the Kleenex tissue maker said.
